thursday 
rice the contests originator called vernons purple prose 
an example of a writer getting carried away with figures of 
speech 
if youre reading aloud take a breath and give it a try 
dolores breezed along the surface of her life like a flat 
stone forever skipping along smooth water rippling reality 
sporadically but oblivious to it consistently until she finally 
lost momentum sank and due to an overdose of fluoride as a child 
which caused her to suffer from chronic apathy doomed herself to 
