recorded at 914 pm determined the epicenter to be 372 miles 
northeast of pyongyang north korea 
no further details were available 
the richter scale is a gauge of the energy released by an 
earthquake as measured by ground motion recorded on a seismograph 
every increase of one number means that the ground motion is 10 
times greater a quake of magnitude 5 can cause serious damage on 
land and a quake measuring 6 can cause severe damage 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

